ally, mediclaim costs some moneyMoney depends on age of the personYour mom is 44 so it might costs like 30k-35k a year for the mediclaim of amount 4- 5 lakhsI am guessing this amount it can be little more or lessSo if company covers the mediclaim then they pay it from our total CTC or some part of money the also pay to the mediclaim companyIdeally it's all taken care by company","time":"May 17, 2024 11:57 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Ideally they shouldn'tIt depends on how much the mediclaim coverage is","time":"May 17, 2024 11:58 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Got ittt","time":"May 17, 2024 11:59 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"She said I have to pay it","time":"May 17, 2024 11:59 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Like normally we get the claim","time":"May 17, 2024 11:59 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Will you have to pay the cost of mediclaim only","time":"May 18, 2024 12:00 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"She doesn’t make any sense","time":"May 18, 2024 12:00 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Do you have HR number maa6","time":"May 18, 2024 12:00 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Do you have HR number ma'am (edited)","time":"May 18, 2024 12:01 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I’ll ask again","time":"May 18, 2024 12:01 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"It’s really tiring to even talk","time":"May 18, 2024 12:02 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"To her","time":"May 18, 2024 12:02 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"She tells you everything but what’s needed","time":"May 18, 2024 12:02 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Ask these questions1) dies company provides mediclaim and if it does dies it cover parents as well2) if it covers parents what's the policy amount3) what's the tpa name","time":"May 18, 2024 12:03 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"B